AttributeList.Text: ##This is a fieldbus value. get from inverter, if we need it.
HBL_TT_21 Oil sump wall temperature left
HBL_TT_22 Oil sump wall temperature right
HBL_TT_23 Compressor motor U winding temperatue
HBL_TT_24 Compressor motor V winding temperature
HBL_TT_25 Compressor motor W winding temperature

MAX of any of the winding temperatures. If there is only one motor temperature, eg one PTC, use HBL-TT-20 as the analog input object The individual winding temperatures are not used in the program (but are available for monitoring & logging)
HBL_TT_26 Compressor motor D bearing temperature
HBL_TT_27 Compressor motor N bearing temperature
